    "description": "Lost In Static是一款第一人称心理恐怖体验。探索一个超现实且令人不安的购物中心，在这里现实模糊，理智脆弱。你本该和女儿一起享受一个简单的外出日，但在你失去意识后，你醒来并进入了后室。<strong>你的任务？找到你的女儿，然后逃离这里。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点: </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>电视遥控器</strong>: 允许你在地图上传送。<br></li><li><strong>笔记</strong>: 提供生存的线索和提示，了解过去。<br></li><li><strong>边缘空间:</strong> 导航边缘空间走廊。<br></li><li><strong>生存:</strong> 躲避异常实体。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使用电视传送: </strong></h2>地图上有一些故障的电视。操纵它们的波长进行传送。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/34d3cf0ab5341b60919929f2009b8986.poster.avif?t=1768880508\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/34d3cf0ab5341b60919929f2009b8986.webm?t=1768880508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/34d3cf0ab5341b60919929f2009b8986.mp4?t=1768880508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>跟随笔记: </strong></h2>阅读笔记，了解发生了什么，或者找到如何逃生的提示。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/981181d03c6448dc47beb1973eb84a03.poster.avif?t=1768880508\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/981181d03c6448dc47beb1973eb84a03.webm?t=1768880508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/981181d03c6448dc47beb1973eb84a03.mp4?t=1768880508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿越边缘空间: </strong></h2>穿过边缘空间，尽量不要被抓住。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5a1bcf6f9f35dba48693441bd836c48e.poster.avif?t=1768880508\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5a1bcf6f9f35dba48693441bd836c48e.webm?t=1768880508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5a1bcf6f9f35dba48693441bd836c48e.mp4?t=1768880508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>逃离你遇到的异常实体: </strong></h2>你不是唯一一个有任务的东西。小心各种生物。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5d04d332ea89a3c1b2fe2a33a5044b13.poster.avif?t=1768880508\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5d04d332ea89a3c1b2fe2a33a5044b13.webm?t=1768880508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5d04d332ea89a3c1b2fe2a33a5044b13.mp4?t=1768880508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
